// Talons
LF_DRIVE_PORT       1               /**< Left F drive Talon                 */
RF_DRIVE_PORT       2               /**< Right F drive Talon                */
LR_DRIVE_PORT       3               /**< Left R drive Talon                 */
RR_DRIVE_PORT       4               /**< Right R drive Talon                */
WINCH_PORT          5               /**< Winch talon                        */
BALLAQ_WINDIN       6               /**< Talon to wind balls into the shooter */
DEFENSE_MOTOR       7               /**< Talon to wind up and down the pole */

// Relays
COMPRESSOR_PORT     1               /**< Compressor relay port              */

// DIO
PRESSURE_SWITCH     1               /**< Pressure switch DIO port           */
WINCH_HARDSTOP      2               /**< Digital input for the winch limit switch */

// Analog
LOADCELL_CHANNEL    1               /**< Loadcell analog channel            */

// Pneumatics
WINCH_RELEASE_PORT  1               /**< Piston that quickreleases the winch */
BALLAQ_DEPLOY       2               /**< Piston port to extend the ball aq  */
BALLAQ_UNDEPLOY     3               /**< Piston port to retract the ball aq */


// CONTROLS:
LX -> Mecanum Strafe
LY -> Mecanum F/R
RX -> Mecanum Rotate

A -> Defense down
Y -> Defense up

Right bumper -> Deploy ball aq
Left bumper -> Retract ball aq

Left trigger -> Wind ball aq
Right trigger -> Fire the shooter

D-pad up -> Adjust desired voltage up
D-pad down -> Adjust desired voltage down
